{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5df82c462c","title":"关于推迟召开全国计划会议问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"71521f0569","index":0,"year":1959,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"5df82c462c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"7b04c51715","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5df82c462c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央书记处书记、国务院副总理兼国家计划委员会主任季富春1959年10月9日晚给周恩来并毛泽东、中央的报告上。报告说：（一）国家计委关于拟订1960年国民经济计划大纲的报告，已根据政治局初步讨论的意见作了修改补充，如中央觉得原则上还可以，建议批转下去，作为编制明年计划草案的依据之一。（二）建议在本月18日召开全国计划会议，讨论今年的经济形势和明年计划的方针、任务，拟出明年计划的草案。"},{"id":"fca74a058a","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5df82c462c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"93657e13c0","type":"title","text":"关于推退召开全国计划会议问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5df82c462c"},{"id":"7b04c51715","type":"paragraph","text":"即退李富春同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5df82c462c"},{"id":"fca74a058a","type":"paragraph","text":"此件今天才收到，故计划会议时间宜改十月廿四日，以便计划大纲草案有时间送达地方并加以研究，再来开会。如同意，请即交尚昆办理。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5df82c462c"},{"id":"708d7ffc9e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5df82c462c"},{"id":"817c1d53b3","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十五日下午二时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5df82c462c"}],"page":{"id":"36957f8279","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"5df82c462c","start":442,"end":442}}}},"__N_SSG":true}